      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It has been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape. It\u2019s super clean, runs great, and is totally ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute. I've taken great care of it, and I think you're really going to love how it drives. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
