    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension features refreshed bushings and updated dampers for precise lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A mechanically sorted specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
