    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor, honest character marks of careful road use, such as a few light stone chips on the hood. The alloy wheels are free of major curbing and are wrapped in tires with significant tread life remaining. Step inside to a cabin that has been smoke-free and fastidiously kept; the leather seating is supple with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, reflecting a history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. On the road, the car feels tight and composed, with smooth gear transitions and a responsive braking system that inspires confidence. This is a complete, turn-key package for someone who appreciates a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
